OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FAny
OL,6,Fpatchy early cloud clearing Thursday
OL,7,Fand Friday to give long sunny spells.
OL,8,FBreezy Thursday, easing Friday.
OL,9,FCloudier Saturday, with sunny
OL,10,Fintervals and a risk of showers.
OL,11,FTemperatures increasing.
